sbmlme.converter

Class MEJsonMetaboliteType

  • java.lang.Object
    • sbmlme.converter.MEJsonMetaboliteType

  • public class MEJsonMetaboliteType
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the species type in a COBRAme model. Any species in a COBRAme model needs to have one and only one of the declared types in this class.
    Author:
    Marc A. Voigt
